Review: I could rate this 1 star or 5 stars this was so batshit crazy….

Honestly so good so camp so deeply upsetting! Everyone is capital A Acting here!!!! That last “do you understand me?” From Julianne and that last “it’s getting more real” from Natalie is sooooo chilling….
Obviously very good but I have to say they really could have shaved down an hour… I’m sorry Thelma I love you but please!!!

Seeing this in the theater…. TRANSCENDENT EXPERIENCE!!!!!! I forgot just how Unhinged this movie is, my god….I am just so so so obsessed with this and so happy it exists and I wish we had more movies that just go full fucking insane and make up a crazy story and just GO FOR IT!!! That’s what the movies are all about baby! Catherine keener is so fucking sexy being mean in her monochrome outfits…… I miss Cameron Diaz in…
Movies used to have Adam Goldberg in them…..
this years annual Christmas Day movie w the fam!! Every frame for real a painting….

Oh dear I do fear my Timothée was miscast, but his singing was darling most of the time and especially in the last song his voice cracks for a second at the emotional high, I loved that! Some great performances and some just soooo bad. Hated the VFX as per usual
Sarah Jessica Parker for some reason smells a bar of soap seductively in one scene for seemingly no reason???????? Rachel mcadams soooooooo hot in this though like the NPR tote bag? Fuck OFF!!!!!!
And if I said this was my favourite Coppola movie ever….. what then….. like my god, it’s sinister and thrilling and beautiful and quiet and the light leaks in so gorgeously…

I love the wara wara so much and the pelicans and the parakeets!!! And the heron! So many beautiful birds!!! honestly this whole movie was mesmerizing - mature but readable for a child I think? Idk! I hope it wins the Oscar……. But I know something silly made by Disney will obviously win instead… I HOPE I AM WRONG!!!
